      "slug": "lakoff-and-johnson",
      "title": "Lakoff And Johnson",
      "text": "Lakoff and Johnson are the authors of an outstanding and accessible introduction to [[Conceptual Metaphor]] titled [[Metaphors We Live By]]. It belongs on everyone's [[Book List]]."
